This repository contains the documentation, configuration, and submission
metadata for the JassWiki MCP server.

DOCUMENTATION (this repository):  Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
                                  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

CONTENT served by the MCP server: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
                                  Source: https://jasswiki.ch
                                  Attribution: JassWiki.ch / Remo Prinz

ATTESTATION DOCUMENTS:            Public domain (CC0)
                                  did.json, mcp-authority.json, server-card.json

The MCP server software itself (private implementation) is not licensed for
public reuse. The server is operated as a public service.
